Draw the layout of the beds of your garden and start planning month for month and year for year the plants and fertilizers for each bed.
Based on JavaFX 1.3.1 with libraries for Windows.
Unfortunately, with JavaFX 1.3.1 it's not possible to create one jar-file running on multiple plattforms, because the JREs don't support this version of JavaFX.

The running application can be downloaded here:
http://www.ergon.ch/mitarbeiter/MeyerAlbin/gartenplaner.html